Paul Nicholls (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Paul_Nicholls_(actor) 0 Paul Nicholls (born Gerrard Paul Greenhalgh on 12 April 1979) is an English actor from Bolton, Greater Manchester, England. He is best known for his roles as Joe Wicks in BBC's EastEnders, DS Sam Casey in ITV's Law Order: UK, and Steve Bell in Channel 4's Ackley Bridge.
